{"tid":844780,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英媒爆料︰同摩佬有你冇我 普巴威脅1月走人","createTime":"2018-10-02T06:41:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T07:34:24.000Z","uid":37875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bdd3a624fd94ff7fc3ad7cf5197f2e4ca9db0586","tid":844780,"uid":37875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:41:29.000Z","msg":"曼聯球星保羅普巴與領隊摩連奴關係勢成水火，據英國《太陽報》報道，普巴表示除非摩連奴走人，否則他將於1月離開曼聯。<br />\n摩連奴剛表示不相信自己將會被炒，但英國《太陽報》報道，該名盛傳與摩連奴不和的法國球星已告訴隊友們，他已懶得再跟摩佬爭拗。報道說2016年夏天以8,900萬鎊轉會費由祖雲達斯加盟曼聯的普巴，今季與摩連奴發生連串衝突，上周更被褫副隊長之職，現在他已不得不接受他根本無法在這名領隊麾下比賽的事實，如摩連奴繼續留下他想離隊。<br />\n--------------------<br />\n荷蘭殺神[紅SP]戴維斯參戰確定！立即下載 BFB CHAMPIONS 2.0，建立你的橙衫軍！ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xrTKGM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xrTKGM&d=GBi8YXmaH8y%2Brevsq%2Fz6V9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=90efdd2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xrTKGM</a> <br />\n--------------------<br />\n《體蘋果》陪你睇波講波<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fb.com/appledailysports\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fb.com%2Fappledailysports&d=GBi8YXmaH8y%2Brevsq%2Fz6V9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=689ebb27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.fb.com/appledailysports</a>  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\nC朗涉強姦案 LV警方重啟調查<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【戰果速遞】主場被基達菲逼和 切爾達四場不勝"},{"pid":"f2ac5079158303bf10d73c57c13dc922a586d764","tid":844780,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"摩廢奴同普巴獸都係兩件水貨，邊個接？"},{"pid":"b208851b3e579054a13a77be10f5086f64865e74","tid":844780,"uid":15053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:00:56.000Z","msg":"2個都不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24da7b2a5c8230abe603eb754c2e71b1f53189b0","tid":844780,"uid":13718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:22:47.000Z","msg":"兩個都要炒尻哂啦<im